def udeo_ostrvo(prozor):
    #   
    cg = 1
    nekod = 1
    
    #   
    k = len(prozor)
    
    #     
    for i in range(k-1):
        #   
        p = prozor[i:i+2]
        
        #   
        cg    *= p_cg[p]
        nekod *= p_nekod[p]
    
    #   
    return cg > nekod

def cg_prozor(dnk, k, cg_ostrvo):
    #    
    print(dnk)
    
    #   
    n = len(dnk)
    
    #   
    predlog = ''
    
    #    
    for i in range(n-k+1):
        #   
        prozor = dnk[i:i+k]
        
        #      
        if i < (n-k+1)/2:
            print(i    *' ', '\r' if not i else '', sep='', end='')
        else:
            print((i-4)*' ', sep='', end='')
        
        #      CG 
        ostrvo = cg_ostrvo(prozor)
        
        #      
        predlog = predlog + ('+' if ostrvo else '-')
        
        #     +  -
        if i < (n-k+1)/2:
            print(prozor, f'({predlog[-1]})')
        else:
            print(f'({predlog[-1]})', prozor)
    
    #     
    predlog = (k-1)//2 * predlog[0] + \
              predlog + \
              (k-1)//2 * predlog[-1]
    
    #    
    print(dnk)
    
    #    
    print(predlog)
    
    #   
    return predlog

#    HMM  
def proveri(hmm):
    #   
    polazne = sum(hmm.pi)
    
    #   
    if not blisko(polazne, 1):
        return False
    
    #     
    for i in range(hmm.n):
        #   
        prelazi = sum(hmm.a[i])
        
        #   
        if not blisko(prelazi, 1):
            return False
        
        #   
        emisije = sum(hmm.b[i])
        
        #   
        if not blisko(emisije, 1):
            return False
    
    #    
    return True

class HMM:
    #  HMM   
    def __init__(hmm, a, b, pi=None):
        #   
        if pi is None:
            pi = {xi: 1/len(a) for xi in a}
        
        #    
        hmm.a = a
        hmm.b = b
        hmm.pi = pi
        
        #    
        hmm.a[''] = pi
        
        #     
        hmm.x = list(a)
        hmm.x.remove('')
        hmm.n = len(hmm.x)
        
        #     
        hmm.y = list(b[hmm.x[0]])
        hmm.m = len(hmm.y)
        
        #   -
        hmm.pi_log = {xi: log(pi[xi]) for xi in hmm.x}
        hmm.a_log  = {xi: {xj: log(a[xi][xj]) for xj in hmm.x} for xi in hmm.x}
        hmm.b_log  = {xi: {yj: log(b[xi][yj]) for yj in hmm.y} for xi in hmm.x}
        
        #    -
        hmm.a_log[''] = hmm.pi_log

def svi_putevi(hmm, k, p=None, i=0):
    #   
    if not p:
        p = [''] * k
    
    #     
    if i == k:
        yield ''.join(p)
    else:
        #    
        for xi in hmm.x:
            p[i] = xi
            
            #   
            yield from svi_putevi(hmm, k, p, i+1)

def naivno_dekodiranje(hmm, o, logg=False):

def viterbi_graf(x, tau, k):
    #   
    if not k: return 0
    
    #  ()
    s = {xi: [tau('', xi)] for xi in x}
    
    #  ()
    for t in range(1, k):
        for xi in x:
            s[xi].append(max(s[xj][t-1] + tau(xj, xi, t) for xj in x))
    
    #  ()
    return max(s[xj][k-1] + tau(xj, '') for xj in x)

def viterbi_dekodiranje(hmm, o):
    #   
    k = len(o)
    
    #   
    if not k: return 1, ''
    
    #  
    s = {xi: [hmm.pi[xi] * hmm.b[xi][o[0]]] for xi in hmm.x}
    
    #  
    p = {xi: [xi, ''] for xi in hmm.x}
    
    #   
    for t in range(1, k):
        #    
        for xi in hmm.x:
            #    
            x_opt = hmm.x[0]
            sx_opt = s[x_opt][t-1] * hmm.a[x_opt][xi] * hmm.b[xi][o[t]]
            
            #    
            for j in range(1, hmm.n):
                xj = hmm.x[j]
                sxi = s[xj][t-1] * hmm.a[xj][xi] * hmm.b[xi][o[t]]
                
                #    
                if sxi > sx_opt:
                    sx_opt = sxi
                    x_opt = xj
            
            #   
            s[xi].append(sx_opt)
            
            #   
            p[xi][1] = p[x_opt][0] + xi
        
        #   
        for xi in hmm.x:
            p[xi][0] = p[xi][1]
        
    #  ; 
    #    
    x_opt = hmm.x[0]
    sx_opt = s[x_opt][k-1]
    
    #    
    for j in range(1, hmm.n):
        xj = hmm.x[j]
        sxj = s[xj][k-1]
        
        #    
        if sxj > sx_opt:
            sx_opt = sxj
            x_opt = xj
    
    #   
    return sx_opt, p[x_opt][0]

def opt_ops_na_putu(hmm, p):
    #   
    k = len(p)
    
    #  
    o = ''
    p_o = 1
    
    #    
    for i in range(k):
        #    
        y_opt = hmm.y[0]
        p_opt = hmm.b[p[i]][y_opt]
        
        #    
        for j in range(1, hmm.m):
            yj = hmm.y[j]
            pj = hmm.b[p[i]][y_opt]
            
            #     
            if pj > p_opt:
                p_opt = pj
                y_opt = y_j
        
        #   
        o = o + y_opt
        p_o *= p_opt
    
    #   
    return p_o, o

def uzorkuj(hmm, k, seme=None):
    #     
    if not k: return '', ''
    
    #   
    seed(seme)
    
    #    
    p = choice(hmm.x, p=[*hmm.pi.values()])
    
    #     
    o = choice(hmm.y, p=[*hmm.b[p[-1]].values()])
    
    #    
    for _ in range(1, k):
        #    
        p = p + choice(hmm.x, p=[*hmm.a[p[-1]].values()])
        
        #   
        o = o + choice(hmm.y, p=[*hmm.b[p[-1]].values()])
    
    #   
    return p, o

def precisti(P, theta):
    #   
    n = len(P[0])
    
    #   
    m = len(P)
    
    #     
    udeo = [sum(P[i][j] == '-' for i in range(m))
            < m * theta for j in range(n)]
    
    #    
    return [''.join(P[i][j] for j in range(n) if udeo[j]) for i in range(m)], udeo

def profil(P):
    #   
    n = len(P[0])
    
    #   
    m = len(P)
    
    #  
    azbuka = sorted(set(P[i][j] for i in range(m) for j in range(n)))
    
    #   
    if '-' in azbuka:
        azbuka.remove('-')
    
    #      
    prof = {slovo: [sum(P[i][j] == slovo for i in range(m))
                    for j in range(n)] for slovo in azbuka}
    
    #     
    return {slovo: [prof[slovo][j]/sum(prof[s][j] for s in azbuka)
                    for j in range(n)] for slovo in azbuka}

#    
def putevi(P, theta):
    #  
    Pp, udeo = precisti(P, theta)
    
    #     
    Ps = [['S'] for i in range(len(Pp))]
    
    #   
    ui = 0
    
    #    
    for j, u in enumerate(udeo):
        #   
        if u: ui += 1
        
        #    
        for i in range(len(Pp)):
            #   
            if u:
                #   
                if P[i][j] == '-':
                    Ps[i].append(f'D{ui}')
                #   
                else:
                    Ps[i].append(f'M{ui}')
            #   
            elif P[i][j] != '-':
                Ps[i].append(f'I{ui}')
    
    #     
    return [[*Ps[i], 'E'] for i in range(len(Pp))]

#   
def parametri(P, putevi, y=None):
    #   
    n = int(putevi[-1][-2][1:])
    
    #     
    if y is None:
        y = [*profil(P).keys()]
    
    #   
    m = len(y)
    
    #    {S, Ii, Mi, Di, E}
    x = ['S', 'I0', *(f'{X}{i}' for i in range(1, n+1) for X in ('M', 'D', 'I')), 'E']
    
    #   
    a = {xi: {xj: 0 for xj in x} for xi in x}
    
    #   
    b = {xi: {yi: 0 for yi in y} for xi in x}
    
    #   
    for put, ops in zip(putevi, P):
        #    
        ops = ''.join(c for c in ops if c != '-')
        
        #   
        i = 0
        
        #   
        for p1, p2 in windowed(put, 2):
            a[p1][p2] += 1
            
            #   
            if p2 != 'E' and p2[0] != 'D':
                b[p2][ops[i]] += 1
                
                #  
                i += 1
    
    #   
    a = {xi: {xj: a[xi][xj]/sum(a[xi].values()) if
         sum(a[xi].values()) else 0 for xj in x} for xi in x}
    
    #   
    b = {xi: {yj: b[xi][yj]/sum(b[xi].values()) if
         sum(b[xi].values()) else 0 for yj in y} for xi in x}
    
    #   
    return a, b

#  
def ok(xi, xj, n):
    #     
    if xi == 'S':
        return xj in ('I0', 'M1', 'D1')
    #     
    elif xj == 'E':
        return xi in (f'I{n}', f'M{n}', f'D{n}')
    #    
    elif xi == 'E' or xj == 'S':
        return False
    
    #   
    i = int(xi[1:])
    j = int(xj[1:])
    
    #   
    xi = xi[0]
    xj = xj[0]
    
    #   
    if i == j:
        return xj == 'I'
    #    
    elif i+1 == j:
        return xj == 'M' or xj == 'D'
    #    
    else: return False

#     
class ProfHMM:
    #   
    def __init__(self, P, theta, sigma, y=None):
        #   
        puts = putevi(P, theta)
        
        #   
        a, b = parametri(P, puts, y)
        
        #   
        self.n = len(a) // 3 - 1
        
        #  
        a = {xi: {xj: a[xi][xj] + sigma if ok(xi, xj, self.n)
                      else 0 for xj in a[xi]} for xi in a}
        b = {xi: {yj: b[xi][yj] + sigma if xi[0] not in ('S', 'E', 'D')
                      else 0 for yj in b[xi]} for xi in b}
        
        #  
        self.a = {xi: {xj: a[xi][xj]/sum(a[xi].values()) if sum(a[xi].\
                    values()) else 0 for xj in a[xi]} for xi in a}
        self.b = {xi: {yj: b[xi][yj]/sum(b[xi].values()) if sum(b[xi].\
                    values()) else 0 for yj in b[xi]} for xi in b}
        
        #  
        self.x = [*self.a]
        
        #  
        self.y = [*self.b[self.x[0]]]
        
        #   
        self.m = len(self.y)

def poravnanje(ops, put):
    #  
    i, por = 0, ''
    
    #     
    for p in put:
        #    
        if p[0] == 'M':
            por = por + ops[i]
            
            #  
            i += 1
        
        #    
        elif p[0] == 'I':
            por = por + colored(ops[i], 'red')
            
            #  
            i += 1
        
        #    
        elif p[0] == 'D':
            por = por + '-'
    
    #  
    return por

def viterbi_prof(hmm, o):
    #   
    k = len(o)
    
    #    
    o = '-' + o
    
    #   
    x, n, y, m, a, b = hmm.x, hmm.n, hmm.y, hmm.m, hmm.a, hmm.b
    
    #   
    s = {xi: [None] for xi in x}
    
    #  
    p = {xi: [['S', xi], ['S', xi]] for xi in x}
    
    #   
    s['D1'][0] = a['S']['D1']
    
    #    
    for i in range(2, n+1):
        #  
        s[f'D{i}'][0] = s[f'D{i-1}'][0] * a[f'D{i-1}'][f'D{i}']
        
        #    
        p[f'D{i}'][0] = p[f'D{i-1}'][0] + [f'D{i}']
    
    #      
    if not k:
        return s[f'D{n}'][0] * a[f'D{n}']['E'], p[f'D{n}'][0] + ['E']
    
    #   
    for t in range(1, k+1):
        #   
        for i in range(n+1):
            #    
            for Y in ('M', 'D', 'I'):       
                #   
                Y = f'{Y}{i}'
                
                #    
                if t == 1:
                    #    I0
                    if Y == 'I0':
                        s['I0'].append(a['S']['I0'] * b['I0'][o[t]])
                    
                    #    M1
                    if Y == 'M1':

def forward_prof(hmm, o):
    #   
    k = len(o)
    
    #    
    o = '-' + o
    
    #   
    x, n, y, m, a, b = hmm.x, hmm.n, hmm.y, hmm.m, hmm.a, hmm.b
    
    #   
    s = {xi: [None] for xi in x}
    
    #   
    s['D1'][0] = a['S']['D1']
    
    #    
    for i in range(2, n+1):
        #  
        s[f'D{i}'][0] = s[f'D{i-1}'][0] * a[f'D{i-1}'][f'D{i}']
    
    #      
    if not k:
        return s[f'D{n}'][0] * a[f'D{n}']['E']
    
    #   
    for t in range(1, k+1):
        #   
        for i in range(n+1):
            #    
            for Y in ('M', 'D', 'I'):       
                #   
                Y = f'{Y}{i}'
                
                #    
                if t == 1:
                    #    I0
                    if Y == 'I0':
                        s['I0'].append(a['S']['I0'] * b['I0'][o[t]])
                    
                    #    M1
                    if Y == 'M1':
                        s['M1'].append(a['S']['M1'] * b['M1'][o[t]])
                
                #     :
                #      
                if t == 1 and Y in ('I0', 'M1') \
                   or Y not in s: continue
                
                #   
                sXopt = 0
                
                #    
                for X in ('M', 'D', 'I'):
                    #     
                    if Y[0] == 'I':
                        X = f'{X}{i}'
                    #    
                    else:
                        X = f'{X}{i-1}'
                    
                    #     ;
                    #     
                    if X not in s or X[0] != 'D' and not s[Y][t-1]:
                        continue
                    
                    #      
                    if Y[0] == 'D':
                        sXopt += s[X][t] * a[X][Y]
                    #      
                    else:
                        sXopt += s[X][t-1] * a[X][Y] * b[Y][o[t]]
                
                #   
                s[Y].append(sXopt)
    
    #  ; 
    #   
    return sum(s[f'{X}{n}'][k] * a[f'{X}{n}']['E'] for X in ('M', 'D', 'I'))

def nadgledani_params(p, o, x=None, y=None):
    #   
    if x is None: x = sorted({*p})
    
    #   
    n = len(x)
    
    #   
    if y is None: y = sorted({*o})
    
    #   
    m = len(y)
    
    #   
    k = len(p)
    
    #   
    a = {xi: {xj: 0 for xj in x} for xi in x}
    
    #   
    for i in range(1, k):
        a[p[i-1]][p[i]] += 1
        
    #   
    a = {xi: {xj: a[xi][xj]/sum(a[xi].values()) if sum(a[xi].\
            values()) else 1/n for xj in x} for xi in x}
    
    #   
    b = {xi: {yi: 0 for yi in y} for xi in x}
    
    #   
    for i in range(k):
        b[p[i]][o[i]] += 1
    
    #   
    b = {xi: {yj: b[xi][yj]/sum(b[xi].values()) if sum(b[xi].\
            values()) else 1/m for yj in y} for xi in x}
    
    #   
    return a, b

def backward(hmm, o):
    #   
    k = len(o)
    
    #   
    if not k: return 1, None
    
    #  ()
    w = {xi: k*[1] for xi in hmm.x}
    
    #  ()
    for t in range(k-2, -1, -1):
        for xi in hmm.x:
            w[xi][t] = sum(hmm.a[xi][xj] * hmm.b[xj][o[t+1]] * w[xj][t+1] for xj in hmm.x)
    
    #  ()
    return sum(hmm.pi[xj] * hmm.b[xj][o[0]] * w[xj][0] for xj in hmm.x), w

def log_backward(hmm, o):
    #   
    k = len(o)
    
    #   
    if not k: return 0, None
    
    #  ()
    w_log = {xi: k*[0] for xi in hmm.x}
    
    #  ()
    for t in range(k-2, -1, -1):
        for xi in hmm.x:
            w_log[xi][t] = lse([hmm.a_log[xi][xj] + hmm.b_log[xj][o[t+1]] +
                                w_log[xj][t+1] for xj in hmm.x])
    
    #  ()
    return lse([hmm.pi_log[xj] + hmm.b_log[xj][o[0]] + w_log[xj][0] for xj in hmm.x]), w_log

def fwd_bwd(hmm, o):
    #   
    k = len(o)
    
    #  
    p, f = forward(hmm, o)
    
    #  
    _, w = backward(hmm, o)
    
    #   
    return {xi: [f[xi][t] * w[xi][t] / p for t in range(k)] for xi in hmm.x}

def map_dekodiranje(hmm, o):
    #   
    meko = fwd_bwd(hmm, o)
    
    #   
    x = [*meko]
    
    #

        #

            #

        #

        v *= vt
    
    #   
    return v, p

def fwd_bwd2(hmm, o):
    #   
    k = len(o)
    
    #  
    p, f = forward(hmm, o)
    
    #  
    _, w = backward(hmm, o)
    
    #   
    return {xi: {xj: [f[xi][t] * hmm.a[xi][xj] * hmm.b[xj][o[t+1]] * w[xj][t+1]
                    / p for t in range(k-1)] for xj in hmm.x} for xi in hmm.x}

def e_bw(hmm, o):
    #   
    k = len(o)
    
    #  
    p, f = forward(hmm, o)
    
    #  
    _, w = backward(hmm, o)
    
    #  
    Pz = {xi: [f[xi][t] * w[xi][t] / p for t in range(k)] for xi in hmm.x}

    #  
    Pzz = {xi: {xj: [f[xi][t] * hmm.a[xi][xj] * hmm.b[xj][o[t+1]] * w[xj][t+1]
                    / p for t in range(k-1)] for xj in hmm.x} for xi in hmm.x}
    
    #  
    return Pz, Pzz

def m_bw(hmm, Pz, Pzz, o):
    #   
    k = len(o)
    
    #   
    a = {xi: {xj: sum(Pzz[xi][xj][t] for t in range(k-1)) for xj in hmm.x} for xi in hmm.x}
    
    #   
    a = {xi: {xj: a[xi][xj]/sum(a[xi].values()) if sum(a[xi].\
         values()) else 1/hmm.n for xj in hmm.x} for xi in hmm.x}

    #   
    b = {xi: {yj: sum(o[t] == yj and Pz[xi][t] for t in range(k)) for yj in hmm.y} for xi in hmm.x}
    
    #   
    b = {xi: {yj: b[xi][yj]/sum(b[xi].values()) if sum(b[xi].\
         values()) else 1/hmm.m for yj in hmm.y} for xi in hmm.x}
    
    #  
    return a, b
